{
  "clauseId": "ec20beb11b264c8dba0ee98e643d0a4d",
  "clauseName": "3.1.1.1_农产品精简版（20260422181920）",
  "clauseNumber": "3.1.1.1",
  "clauseContent": "3.1.1.1.  <span style=\"color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">非农产品核定扣除企业申报表填写（附表二）</span>\n<div class=\"quill-better-table-wrapper\"><table class=\"quill-better-table\" style=\"width: 100%;\"><colgroup><col width=\"auto\"><col width=\"auto\"><col width=\"auto\"><col width=\"auto\"></colgroup><tbody><tr data-row=\"1\"><td data-row=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\" data-cell-bg=\"rgb(245, 247, 250)\" style=\"background-color: rgb(245, 247, 250);\"><p class=\"qlbt-cell-line ql-align-center\" data-row=\"1\" data-cell=\"1\" data-rowspan=\"1\" data-colspan=\"1\" data-cell-bg=\"rgb(245, 247, 250)\"><strong style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">栏次</strong></p></td><td data-row=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\" data-cell-bg=\"rgb(245, 247, 250)\" style=\"background-color: rgb(245, 247, 250);\"><p class=\"qlbt-cell-line ql-align-center\" data-row=\"1\" data-cell=\"2\" data-rowspan=\"1\" data-colspan=\"1\" data-cell-bg=\"rgb(245, 247, 250)\"><strong style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">栏次名称</strong></p></td><td data-row=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\" data-cell-bg=\"rgb(245, 247, 250)\" style=\"background-color: rgb(245, 247, 250);\"><p class=\"qlbt-cell-line ql-align-center\" data-row=\"1\" data-cell=\"3\" data-rowspan=\"1\" data-colspan=\"1\" data-cell-bg=\"rgb(245, 247, 250)\"><strong style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">适用发票类型</strong></p></td><td data-row=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\" data-cell-bg=\"rgb(245, 247, 250)\" style=\"background-color: rgb(245, 247, 250);\"><p class=\"qlbt-cell-line ql-align-center\" data-row=\"1\" data-cell=\"4\" data-rowspan=\"1\" data-colspan=\"1\" data-cell-bg=\"rgb(245, 247, 250)\"><strong style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">填写说明与风险提示</strong></p></td></tr><tr data-row=\"2\"><td data-row=\"2\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\"><p class=\"qlbt-cell-line\" data-row=\"2\" data-cell=\"1\" data-rowspan=\"1\" data-colspan=\"1\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">第2栏</span></p></td><td data-row=\"2\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\"><p class=\"qlbt-cell-line\" data-row=\"2\" data-cell=\"2\" data-rowspan=\"1\" data-colspan=\"1\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">本期认证相符且本期申报抵扣</span></p></td><td data-row=\"2\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\"><p class=\"qlbt-cell-line\" data-row=\"2\" data-cell=\"3\" data-rowspan=\"1\" data-colspan=\"1\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">1.&nbsp;增值税专用发票（9%、1%税率）</span></p><p class=\"qlbt-cell-line\" data-row=\"2\" data-cell=\"3\" data-rowspan=\"1\" data-colspan=\"1\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">2.&nbsp;海关进口增值税专用缴款书</span></p></td><td data-row=\"2\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\"><p class=\"qlbt-cell-line\" data-row=\"2\" data-cell=\"4\" data-rowspan=\"1\" data-colspan=\"1\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">按票面注明的税额直接填写。</span><strong style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">注意</strong><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">：1%专票只能按票面税额填此栏，不得按9%计算后填第6栏。</span></p></td></tr><tr data-row=\"3\"><td data-row=\"3\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\"><p class=\"qlbt-cell-line\" data-row=\"3\" data-cell=\"1\" data-rowspan=\"1\" data-colspan=\"1\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">第6栏</span></p></td><td data-row=\"3\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\"><p class=\"qlbt-cell-line\" data-row=\"3\" data-cell=\"2\" data-rowspan=\"1\" data-colspan=\"1\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">农产品收购发票或者销售发票</span></p></td><td data-row=\"3\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\"><p class=\"qlbt-cell-line\" data-row=\"3\" data-cell=\"3\" data-rowspan=\"1\" data-colspan=\"1\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">1.&nbsp;农产品收购发票</span></p><p class=\"qlbt-cell-line\" data-row=\"3\" data-cell=\"3\" data-rowspan=\"1\" data-colspan=\"1\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">2.&nbsp;自产自销免税农产品普通发票（数电票需有标签）</span></p><p class=\"qlbt-cell-line\" data-row=\"3\" data-cell=\"3\" data-rowspan=\"1\" data-colspan=\"1\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">3.&nbsp;小规模纳税人开具的3%专票（按计算抵扣）</span></p><p class=\"qlbt-cell-line\" data-row=\"3\" data-cell=\"3\" data-rowspan=\"1\" data-colspan=\"1\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">4.&nbsp;税务机关代开的自产农产品免税发票</span></p></td><td data-row=\"3\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\"><p class=\"qlbt-cell-line\" data-row=\"3\" data-cell=\"4\" data-rowspan=\"1\" data-colspan=\"1\"><strong style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">核心栏次</strong><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">：填写按买价×9%计算出的进项税额。</span></p><p class=\"qlbt-cell-line\" data-row=\"3\" data-cell=\"4\" data-rowspan=\"1\" data-colspan=\"1\"><strong style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">风险</strong><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">：流通环节免税普票、1%专票、带税率普票均</span><strong style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">不得</strong><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">填入此栏。</span></p></td></tr><tr data-row=\"4\"><td data-row=\"4\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\"><p class=\"qlbt-cell-line\" data-row=\"4\" data-cell=\"1\" data-rowspan=\"1\" data-colspan=\"1\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">第8a栏</span></p></td><td data-row=\"4\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\"><p class=\"qlbt-cell-line\" data-row=\"4\" data-cell=\"2\" data-rowspan=\"1\" data-colspan=\"1\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">加计扣除农产品进项税额</span></p></td><td data-row=\"4\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\"><p class=\"qlbt-cell-line\" data-row=\"4\" data-cell=\"3\" data-rowspan=\"1\" data-colspan=\"1\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">仅限2026年1月1日之前的业务</span></p></td><td data-row=\"4\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\"><p class=\"qlbt-cell-line\" data-row=\"4\" data-cell=\"4\" data-rowspan=\"1\" data-colspan=\"1\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">用于生产13%税率货物的农产品，在生产领用当期加计扣除1%。</span><strong style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">2026年起此栏不再使用</strong><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">。</span></p></td></tr><tr data-row=\"5\"><td data-row=\"5\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\"><p class=\"qlbt-cell-line\" data-row=\"5\" data-cell=\"1\" data-rowspan=\"1\" data-colspan=\"1\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">第14栏</span></p></td><td data-row=\"5\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\"><p class=\"qlbt-cell-line\" data-row=\"5\" data-cell=\"2\" data-rowspan=\"1\" data-colspan=\"1\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">进项税额转出额</span></p></td><td data-row=\"5\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\"><p class=\"qlbt-cell-line\" data-row=\"5\" data-cell=\"3\" data-rowspan=\"1\" data-colspan=\"1\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">已抵扣但用于免税项目</span></p></td><td data-row=\"5\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\"><p class=\"qlbt-cell-line\" data-row=\"5\" data-cell=\"4\" data-rowspan=\"1\" data-colspan=\"1\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">填写转出的税额。</span></p><p class=\"qlbt-cell-line\" data-row=\"5\" data-cell=\"4\" data-rowspan=\"1\" data-colspan=\"1\"><br></p></td></tr><tr data-row=\"6\"><td data-row=\"6\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\"><p class=\"qlbt-cell-line\" data-row=\"6\" data-cell=\"1\" data-rowspan=\"1\" data-colspan=\"1\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">第15栏</span></p></td><td data-row=\"6\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\"><p class=\"qlbt-cell-line\" data-row=\"6\" data-cell=\"2\" data-rowspan=\"1\" data-colspan=\"1\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">进项税额转出额</span></p></td><td data-row=\"6\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\"><p class=\"qlbt-cell-line\" data-row=\"6\" data-cell=\"3\" data-rowspan=\"1\" data-colspan=\"1\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">已抵扣但用于不得抵扣项目（集体福利、个人消费）</span></p></td><td data-row=\"6\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\"><p class=\"qlbt-cell-line\" data-row=\"6\" data-cell=\"4\" data-rowspan=\"1\" data-colspan=\"1\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">填写转出的税额。</span></p></td></tr><tr data-row=\"7\"><td data-row=\"7\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\"><p class=\"qlbt-cell-line\" data-row=\"7\" data-cell=\"1\" data-rowspan=\"1\" data-colspan=\"1\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">第16栏</span></p></td><td data-row=\"7\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\"><p class=\"qlbt-cell-line\" data-row=\"7\" data-cell=\"2\" data-rowspan=\"1\" data-colspan=\"1\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">进项税额转出额</span></p></td><td data-row=\"7\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\"><p class=\"qlbt-cell-line\" data-row=\"7\" data-cell=\"3\" data-rowspan=\"1\" data-colspan=\"1\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">已抵扣但出现非正常损失</span></p></td><td data-row=\"7\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\"><p class=\"qlbt-cell-line\" data-row=\"7\" data-cell=\"4\" data-rowspan=\"1\" data-colspan=\"1\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">填写转出的税额。</span></p></td></tr><tr data-row=\"8\"><td data-row=\"8\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\"><p class=\"qlbt-cell-line\" data-row=\"8\" data-cell=\"1\" data-rowspan=\"1\" data-colspan=\"1\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">第17栏</span></p></td><td data-row=\"8\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\"><p class=\"qlbt-cell-line\" data-row=\"8\" data-cell=\"2\" data-rowspan=\"1\" data-colspan=\"1\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">进项税额转出额</span></p></td><td data-row=\"8\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\"><p class=\"qlbt-cell-line\" data-row=\"8\" data-cell=\"3\" data-rowspan=\"1\" data-colspan=\"1\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">已抵扣但用于简易计税方法征税项目</span></p></td><td data-row=\"8\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\"><p class=\"qlbt-cell-line\" data-row=\"8\" data-cell=\"4\" data-rowspan=\"1\" data-colspan=\"1\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">填写转出的税额。</span></p></td></tr><tr data-row=\"9\"><td data-row=\"9\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\"><p class=\"qlbt-cell-line\" data-row=\"9\" data-cell=\"1\" data-rowspan=\"1\" data-colspan=\"1\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">第23b栏</span></p></td><td data-row=\"9\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\"><p class=\"qlbt-cell-line\" data-row=\"9\" data-cell=\"2\" data-rowspan=\"1\" data-colspan=\"1\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">其他应作进项税额转出的情形</span></p></td><td data-row=\"9\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\"><p class=\"qlbt-cell-line\" data-row=\"9\" data-cell=\"3\" data-rowspan=\"1\" data-colspan=\"1\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">取得红字发票、税务稽查调增转出、不得抵扣非应税交易项目、年度清算调整、长期资产不得抵扣的进项税额</span></p></td><td data-row=\"9\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\"><p class=\"qlbt-cell-line\" data-row=\"9\" data-cell=\"4\" data-rowspan=\"1\" data-colspan=\"1\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">填写红字发票对应的税额或其他应转出额。</span></p><p class=\"qlbt-cell-line\" data-row=\"9\" data-cell=\"4\" data-rowspan=\"1\" data-colspan=\"1\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">从2026年1月所属期开始，附表二23b“其他应作进项税额转出的情形”栏次不能直接填写了，点击该栏次后会有弹框，在弹框中填写数据后，小计栏次的数据将自动提取到附表二23b栏了。</span></p></td></tr><tr data-row=\"10\"><td data-row=\"10\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\"><p class=\"qlbt-cell-line\" data-row=\"10\" data-cell=\"1\" data-rowspan=\"1\" data-colspan=\"1\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">第31栏</span></p></td><td data-row=\"10\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\"><p class=\"qlbt-cell-line\" data-row=\"10\" data-cell=\"2\" data-rowspan=\"1\" data-colspan=\"1\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">农产品收购发票或者销售发票</span></p></td><td data-row=\"10\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\"><p class=\"qlbt-cell-line\" data-row=\"10\" data-cell=\"3\" data-rowspan=\"1\" data-colspan=\"1\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">未申报抵扣的农产品发票</span></p></td><td data-row=\"10\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\"><p class=\"qlbt-cell-line\" data-row=\"10\" data-cell=\"4\" data-rowspan=\"1\" data-colspan=\"1\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">当企业已取得发票但暂不抵扣时，填入此栏；待实际抵扣时，再从第6栏抵扣（以单张发票为单位，不可拆分）。</span></p></td></tr></tbody></table>",
